{"tid":1703973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新職業解鎖：魔音法師","createTime":"2019-11-10T13:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T13:49:31.000Z","uid":325594,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"117c918553c06db5743ea177304177ff709da68d","tid":1703973,"uid":325594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:43:52.000Z","msg":"我諗大家都記得之前有個喇叭係班癲狗既虐待下壯烈犧牲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DzDokUdpdSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDzDokUdpdSU&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=ac766f5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DzDokUdpdSU</a><br />\n令我醒覺到原來每人都可以做到魔音法師，和理非終於都搵到自己既職業喇，冷氣軍師又可以涼住冷氣做番d野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個小型喇叭係鴨記只係賣$100-$200左右，就已經具備錄音及USB功能。放係到播就得，唔使自己嗌，岩曬我地呢d聲唔夠大既手足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢排班狗咁鍾意入屋村，大家千奇唔好每個人屋企都用個喇叭播野屌狗呀，又或者比d恐怖音樂佢哋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TgU2DUfk31U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTgU2DUfk31U&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=f9318c46\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TgU2DUfk31U</a><br />\n佢又搵唔到你係邊到，如果多d人播整個環迴立體聲，班狗真係會精神失常嫁，可能會射爆曬d玻璃，到時唔覺意同藍絲攬炒埋一份就唔好啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋選舉期就到啦，大家千奇唔好係班建制狗係樓下宣傳個陣係樓上用喇叭屌佢呀，佢真係會唔識反應嫁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌仔第一次開post，求下大家幫手推，一齊討論下點先可以做到個成功既魔音法師。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0784a180b7c04dded06f75fea7b78a0da49baee7","tid":1703973,"uid":2156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:44:19.000Z","msg":"CHINA<br />\n- Completely withdraw extradition bill<br />\n- Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n- Independent commission of inquiry<br />\n- No riot labeling<br />\n- Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nC.H.I.N.A.<br />\nFive demands Not one less"},{"pid":"bf6a4a718fa10354c1ef1edcd02a9f3b739f95b8","tid":1703973,"uid":82553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:46:37.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c8910989b95b1241f5d69287efe7216f5f0071c7","tid":1703973,"uid":313203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:46:58.000Z","msg":"CHINA<br />\n-&nbsp;Completely withdraw extradition bill<br />\n-&nbsp;Holistic withdrawal of unjust charges<br />\n-&nbsp;Independent commission of inquiry<br />\n-&nbsp;No riot labelling<br />\n-&nbsp;Authentic universal suffrage<br />\n<br />\nMake&nbsp;C.H.I.N.A.&nbsp;a censored word."},{"pid":"08f9966531b11b3037160ced4cb13ed3b13a3eb8","tid":1703973,"uid":164752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"117c918553c06db5743ea177304177ff709da68d","tid":1703973,"uid":325594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T13:43:52.000Z","msg":"我諗大家都記得之前有個喇叭係班癲狗既虐待下壯烈犧牲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DzDokUdpdSU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDzDokUdpdSU&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=ac766f5e\" target